Library of Drm features, including modular drm api.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
lib_uree_mtk_modular_drm will be used by modular drm, including acquire secure buffer and decrypt.
Without them, modular drm will not work.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1. libutils.so
2. libcutils.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'system/lib' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
lib_uree_mtk_modular_drm provides interface of modular drm, it is built library.
